OL,3,CWolfhound features on new
OL,4,C'unmistakably Irish' passport
OL,6,FThe Irish wolfhound features
OL,7,Fprominently on Ireland's new passport,
OL,8,Ffollowing a public consultation
OL,9,Finvolving 15,000 people.
OL,11,FThe newly designed passport, launched
OL,12,Fon Friday by Foreign Affairs Minister
OL,13,FHelen McEntee, is being described by
OL,14,Fthe Government as "one of the world's
OL,15,Fmost advanced travel documents".
OL,17,FArtwork in the new passport is
OL,18,Finspired by Ireland's heritage,
OL,19,Fhistory and culture ` with designs
OL,20,Fchosen by the public as part of a
OL,21,Fnationwide consultation.
OL,26,@vD@SOUwD@_O]
