PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782436704
OL,3,CWolfhound features on new
OL,4,C'unmistakably Irish' passport
OL,6,FThe Department of Foreign Affairs said
OL,7,F15,000 people took part in the
OL,8,Fconsultation ` which identified the
OL,9,FIrish wolfhound as a favourite.
OL,11,FIt said the passport maintains the
OL,12,Fhighest international standards of
OL,13,Fdocument security ` and uses
OL,14,Fenvironmentally friendly security inks
OL,15,Fand new production methods.
OL,17,FMs McEntee said the document gives
OL,18,FIrish citizens visa-free access to 186
OL,19,Fcountries.
