FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1782436704
OL,3,CWolfhound features on new
OL,4,C'unmistakably Irish' passport
OL,6,FOn the refresh, she said: "It combines
OL,7,Fsome of the world's most advanced
OL,8,Fsecurity technology with a design that
OL,9,Fproudly reflects who we are as a
OL,10,Fnation, our heritage, creativity and
OL,11,Fnatural beauty."
OL,13,FShe added: "Together with Irish
OL,14,Fcompanies and artists, we have created
OL,15,Fa travel document that is both
OL,16,Ftechnically outstanding and
OL,17,Funmistakably Irish."
OL,19,FThe new passport is available from
OL,20,FFriday.
